    <thetext>Description of problem:
Attempt to move a message to another folder within Evo when running under Wayland. The message gets copied instead.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
evolution-3.20.3-1.fc24.x86_64

How reproducible:
Always.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Run Evo under Wayland.
2. Move a message to another folder.


Actual results:
Message gets copied instead.

Expected results:
Under X, message gets moved.

Additional info:</thetext>
